        <item>
            <title>Vision Pro 開發用連線售 $2,300   外媒：只是一條昂貴的 USB-2.0 數據線</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/13/apple-vision-pro-developer-strap/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-vision-pro-developer-strap</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/13/apple-vision-pro-developer-strap/vr-mr-ar/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 07:15:31 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Vision Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AR/VR]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Vision Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VisionOS]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1219320</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前我們報道過，Vision Pro 需要使用「Developer Strap」專用線材方能夠連接電腦（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/08/apple-vision-pro…w-reset-function/vr-mr-ar/">相關報道</a>），而這條專用線材索價 299 美元（約港幣 2,338 元），同時 Apple 暫時僅向開發者售賣這條線。可是根據外媒報道，這條線實際上傳輸速度比 Wi-Fi 更慢。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1219355" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240208183033-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240208183033-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240208183033.jpg 1277w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/02/06/hands-on-with-the-299-apple-vision-pro-developer-strap-stabler-mac-virtual-display-beta-downgrades-and-more/">9to5mac</a></p><p>據《Apple Insider》報道，Apple 推出「Developer Strap」價值約港幣 2,338 元，用於將 Apple Vision Pro 連接到 Mac。Apple 指這條連接線提供「Apple Vision Pro 和 Mac 之間的 USB-C 連接，有助於加速圖形密集應用和遊戲的開發」，但有開發人員實測過後表示不值得花錢購買這條連接線，而且其效能欠佳。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1219356" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/applevisionprodevelo-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/applevisionprodevelo-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/applevisionprodevelo.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/02/06/hands-on-with-the-299-apple-vision-pro-developer-strap-stabler-mac-virtual-display-beta-downgrades-and-more/">9to5mac</a></p><p>《Apple Insider》引述一名開發人員 Dimitri Bouniol 指，他使用「Developer Strap」連接 Apple Vision Pro 和 Mac 後，發現連接速度僅達 USB-2.0。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1219357" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/applevisionprodevelo-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/applevisionprodevelo-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/applevisionprodevelo-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/02/06/hands-on-with-the-299-apple-vision-pro-developer-strap-stabler-mac-virtual-display-beta-downgrades-and-more/">9to5mac</a></p><p>Dimitri Bouniol 嘗試使用 Apple 官方推出的 0.5m Thunderbolt 3 電線測試，利用 USB 3.2 連接的情況下每秒能夠傳輸 10GB；但如果利用「Developer Strap」要將 4GB 檔案在 Apple Vision Pro 和 Mac 之間傳輸的話，需時大約 107 秒，換算速度為 300 Mbps，與 USB-2.0 的 480 Mbps 理論最高速度相約，因此 Dimitri Boniol 估計 Apple 售賣的「Developer Strap」使用 USB-2.0。</p><p>Apple 沒有透露「Developer Strap」的具體規格，以及傳輸速度。目前尚未有資料顯示傳輸速度到底是被硬件或是軟件拖慢。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://appleinsider.com/articles/24/02/06/300-vision-pro-developer-strap-is-just-an-expensive-usb2-device">Apple Insider</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/13/apple-releases-visionos-1-0-3/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">visionOS 1.0.3 更新，為 Apple Vision Pro 追加密碼重設功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/12/elon-musk-vision-pro-unimpressive/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Elon Musk 試玩 Apple Vision Pro   評價：不是太震撼</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/08/apple-vision-pro-china-launch-april/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Vision Pro 中國推出安排，供應鏈爆料指最快 4 月上市</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/13/apple-vision-pro-developer-strap/vr-mr-ar/">Vision Pro 開發用連線售 $2,300   外媒：只是一條昂貴的 USB-2.0 數據線</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/13/apple-vision-pro-developer-strap/vr-mr-ar/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
